\SE[12]I didn't say anything...! \!\SE[13]I didn't say
anything...!

\SE\SE[15]After we're done, let's go eat dessert. I recommend the
new Maron Custard. \SE[15]That's what I heard.

\SE[16]Leave the support for the leftover group to me!
